{"tid":446984,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"對香港同香港人都無曬希望","createTime":"2017-10-25T00:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T08:55:00.000Z","uid":131332,"like":92,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"41b24e5ee5bc95a0748066372fab0cf841f1fb4f","tid":446984,"uid":131332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:11:02.000Z","msg":"香港人無夢想，日日返工比老闆壓搾，又要唔情願又要做，無曬尊嚴，想買層樓訓下都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人有無諗過返工嘅你同做雞有咩分別？就係做雞都起碼有快感又有錢，而你又無快感又無錢，慘過做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為換左份工會好啲，hea 加有人工出竟然變左主流心態，大陸雞都有目標過香港人<br />\n<br />\n香港人死要面，頂唔順都要扮到無事，自己唔洗活得開心架，人地覺得自己開心就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人比人洗左腦咁，驚死無左份工會餓死，中大食屎生無做嘢咁耐都肥肥白白啦，但香港人自己心態根本好驚去變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當身邊有朋友去改變，香港人心態係希望佢仆街多過希望佢成功。<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔知自己為乜生存。<br />\n<br />\n而家成個香港好有問題，係因為香港人好適合而家個香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我希望自己可以改變自己再影響身邊嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣返去公司遞完辭職信補錢走之後，聽日拎起背囊去流浪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3566fab453a7756a94ef815772daf15c6637bb","tid":446984,"uid":48286,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:20:02.000Z","msg":"咁流浪完之後呢？"},{"pid":"0e9d3e3a0f00c89e17e4b0d1b5901f7b257bf1b4","tid":446984,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:22:28.000Z","msg":"樓主應該係過幾年會後悔自己無啦啦辭左工走去流浪最後搵唔到工既人"},{"pid":"8b879231dd270a37feeab3ea8ae2bd247536a759","tid":446984,"uid":131332,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:26:09.000Z","msg":"流浪過程遇到咩人咩事都唔知，話唔定係其國家遇到真愛，遇到真正想做嘅工作，遇到一齊為夢想奮鬥嘅人，或者我死左都唔知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  比多啲可能自己啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dab22b3d418415f444b32fc7c1d5aa0a6621094","tid":446984,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:30:56.000Z","msg":"實踐吧"},{"pid":"2902fcde74e7d11688e2b5939c3a91258197b8de","tid":446984,"uid":131332,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主應該係過幾年會後悔自己無啦啦辭左工走去流浪最後搵唔到工既人</blockquote><br />\n哈哈，搵唔到咪搵唔到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  總好過乜都未試過就算啊"},{"pid":"4f9e4a416b47009bd281b08ae960e795a640ceec","tid":446984,"uid":131332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>實踐吧</blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9fbabc5b1284f5a180f885d8821c43abea7da7","tid":446984,"uid":101390,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:41:13.000Z","msg":"尋日聽到腦細係度講請人<br />\n話咩大陸請個人5K<br />\n香港請人要投標咁 10K 底價 價低者得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到就知香港已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd454b695e3e12a4f6b