f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 信已遞"},{"pid":"0233311e8e2391a013cfbe012035a4fa72d06279","tid":446984,"uid":9483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"想要夢想就會比其他人針對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8625d82c0662c3e7f8ffb92cd49fcd1bf6cb20","tid":446984,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋日聽到腦細係度講請人<br />\n話咩大陸請個人5K<br />\n香港請人要投標咁 10K 底價 價低者得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到就知香港已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n腦細啊嘛唔好怪人啦"},{"pid":"5a6aa26baedc0ba7fb0240ef01106d793e91ee45","tid":446984,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"諗起之前返pt嗰陣遇到濕鳩老屎忽<br />\n做左一排就唔撈搵過第2份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7171350c2ff40c4ea4d3484679d8611e519cb988","tid":446984,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"成班走去考aco就知啦得啖笑"},{"pid":"a36678e8f1f9fef88404101c556be386803b3c78","tid":446984,"uid":131332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:57:43.000Z","msg":"其實我間公司福利叫唔差，人工好，老闆好睇得起我，我啲客盤都靚仔嘅，但係我真係唔係想要咁嘅生活，我份工機會難得，老闆都覺得好可惜好想留我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到我都好堅決拒絕了"},{"pid":"351f8e2620ffc8437ffd879db1e3402bd31c5d7f","tid":446984,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"同你一樣諗住 辭職流浪<br />\n不過我已做好準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55ed5f8d2757ecf4d17d7acd9bdc0d170aace84","tid":446984,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"有時生活就係太過predictable，所以慣左就唔會想有咩大變化<br />\n<br />\n所以，樓主想做就去做! 去完之後話唔定你會獲得意想唔到既收獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"h